1. Compile and run xv6, a UNIX which is based on Sixth Edition UNIX. It is
probably one of the the most beautiful codes you will come across.

xv6 runs on x86. You can use QEMU to run it.

For more information:
https://pdos.csail.mit.edu/6.828/2016/xv6.html
https://pdos.csail.mit.edu/6.828/2016/xv6.html#v6
http://unix.stackexchange.com/a/266764/106637
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exokernel
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Xv6

